HELL WAS FULL, SO... I'M BACK ♥️☠️🤣 Limited as always, available on the link in my bio now. WOW. What an interesting year. So full of growth & beauty. Of grief, pain & loss. True lessons & blessings. I'm really happy to be leaving my 20's behind to be honest in the new year- (& although I really do believe you are as old as you feel in many ways) - I embrace the ageing process & the wisdom it brings with experience really warmly, & with a deepest gratitude. I think a lot of us were faced with our own shadow this past year, (at least I was) - & I'm really happy to be coming out the other side. This time, I'll really be heeding the advice that has come from such experiences. This next year is a true commitment to my own healing. I'm so sick of my own shit 🤣 Everyone has their own story (all completely incomparable), but for me - being boundaryless was a huge problem. I have always trusted people until they prove me otherwise. (Which is a quality about myself that I also dont want to lose, having a trusting nature in people, & in the universe in general. In everything that has happened / is to come.) However, after people have shown time & time again whether they respect me (or not as it were), I have learnt how to gracefully let go a little earlier than before - before you get cut deep beyond repair. I also had a problem in believing my worth as a human was determined by how much I could serve others. Like if I give everything I have, I will receive love in return. But some of the people I've met over the past 3 years have taken advantage of that so much it's embarassing, & the dumbest thing is that I allowed it all. Repeatedly 😂 I saved too little energy for myself & my own sanity & wellbeing. Nevermore !! SO! Here's to healing, acknowledging & integrating our shadow sides. & ALL the ways in which we could also love people a lot better, with more respect & understanding. I look forward to being even more honest with myself & the people I love the most.

 I'M BACK BITCHEZ. & I AINT DONE YET ☠️

DETAILS 🤤 It's finally all ready!!! On the link in my bio now ✨ the organic classics collection of my lil dreams (not all pictured here, check the site!) 🥲❤️ I have been working on this collection intermittently over the last MONTHS, in between all of chaos & realigning that we have passed. Spent a long time collecting samples & fits, getting the cuts of the pants etc justtt right 👌 Working with our trusted lil family teams of tailors & suppliers to make sure everything will be of the highest quality as always, made with a lot of love & care. The price points are as low as possible for us, because I know what the current climate is like & I honestly always want our stuff to be accessible to the people that vibe with it. EVERYTHING, (including the jewelry) is handmade, ethically and sustainably, to order - & as for the designs themselves, it took a while to get this one together! Adding all the necessary tiny tweaks to bring these simple (yet hopefully v.effective) pieces as close to perfection as possible. I wanted to create some super comfortable pieces that can easily be layered & styled in many different ways, but of a high quality. Timeless classics for your collection, but also pieces that you can really add your own individual sense of styling to. (Which i would fuckin love to see btw, so plz tag me if you order. I really wanna see the looks you come up with 🥲❤️) These are intended to be classic pieces that will last. Pieces that can be dressed up & down as you like. As always, we do make custom size orders at no extra cost if you wanna give us an email, & every item is designed to fit a wide range of sizes anyway, as all pieces are adjustable for a more perfect fit. Dresses all have tie backs which can be cinched to fit, skirts are all of a classic wrap style that are so comfortable for every body shape, & the tops are all super soft & snug. Limited as always. That's enough info i think lol. Love you so much 💘 Thank you a lot for supporting independent & family biznizz xxx

Together Women offers holistic, tailored support to women and girls with multiple & complex needs across Yorkshire and Humberside. Offering support with employment and training, health and wellbeing & housing & homelessness.
